What's about?
=============
This is a simple site for make evolutionary programming using Rails.
Initially, there is a simple list, but you can add requests to see implemented in this site.

How contribute?
===============
There is a project in Rails in a public git repository in site of the github (http://github.com/dadario/ask4more).
Make your clone, implement one of requests to evolve and send the patch to be aggregate in this site.

These are the initial requests:
------------------------------
- Create a dynamic list of requests
- Create a layout for this site

But this list will be deprecated while implements this initial requests
